## 1. What We Are Building

VIDE is an **AI-native creative suite** for video and image editing. Unlike every tool that exists today:

| What Exists | What VIDE Does |
|---|---|
| ShortGPT — automation only, no user footage editing | Full NL editor for existing media |
| InstructPix2Pix — poor object isolation, no undo | SAM2 + DAG edit history |
| Remotion — code-driven, no non-technical users | NL interface over the same engine |
| VlMax — generation only | Editing + generation in one tool |
| twick/editly — API/SDK, no UX | Build the product layer |

**The three unique things NO competitor does together:**
1. A **natural language interface** (text → structured edit plan → execution graph → media output)
2. Editing of the **user's own footage** — not AI-generated content from scratch
3. A fully **non-destructive edit history** — every operation is a DAG node, rewindable, branchable

**The long-vision north star**: A filmmaker types intent in plain language. The system proposes a complete edit plan, executes it as a non-destructive operation graph, lets the filmmaker adjust at any level of abstraction, and exports professional-grade output with proper codecs, audio normalization and color management.

